25std::string WantsToString(const rtc::VideoSinkWants& wants) {
26 rtc::StringBuilder ss;
27
28 ss << "max_fps=" << wants.max_framerate_fps
29 << " max_pixel_count=" << wants.max_pixel_count << " target_pixel_count="
30 << (wants.target_pixel_count.has_value()
31 ? std::to_string(wants.target_pixel_count.value())
32 : "null")
33 << " resolutions={";
34 for (size_t i = 0; i < wants.resolutions.size(); ++i) {
35 if (i != 0)
36 ss << ",";
37 ss << wants.resolutions[i].width << "x" << wants.resolutions[i].height;
38 }
39 ss << "}";
40
41 return ss.Release();
42}

46VideoSourceSinkController::VideoSourceSinkController(
47 rtc::VideoSinkInterface<VideoFrame>* sink,
48 rtc::VideoSourceInterface<VideoFrame>* source)
49 : sink_(sink), source_(source) {
50 RTC_DCHECK(sink_);
51}
52
53VideoSourceSinkController::~VideoSourceSinkController() {
54 RTC_DCHECK_RUN_ON(&sequence_checker_);
55}
56
57void VideoSourceSinkController::SetSource(
58 rtc::VideoSourceInterface<VideoFrame>* source) {
59 RTC_DCHECK_RUN_ON(&sequence_checker_);
60
61 rtc::VideoSourceInterface<VideoFrame>* old_source = source_;
62 source_ = source;
63
64 if (old_source != source && old_source)
65 old_source->RemoveSink(sink_);
66
67 if (!source)
68 return;
69
70 source->AddOrUpdateSink(sink_, CurrentSettingsToSinkWants());
71}
72
73bool VideoSourceSinkController::HasSource() const {
74 RTC_DCHECK_RUN_ON(&sequence_checker_);
75 return source_ != nullptr;
76}
77
78void VideoSourceSinkController::PushSourceSinkSettings() {
79 RTC_DCHECK_RUN_ON(&sequence_checker_);
80 if (!source_)
81 return;
82 rtc::VideoSinkWants wants = CurrentSettingsToSinkWants();
83 RTC_LOG(INFO) << "Pushing SourceSink restrictions: " << WantsToString(wants);
84 source_->AddOrUpdateSink(sink_, wants);
85}

154
155// RTC_EXCLUSIVE_LOCKS_REQUIRED(sequence_checker_)
156rtc::VideoSinkWants VideoSourceSinkController::CurrentSettingsToSinkWants()
157 const {
158 rtc::VideoSinkWants wants;
159 wants.rotation_applied = rotation_applied_;
160 // |wants.black_frames| is not used, it always has its default value false.
161 wants.max_pixel_count =
162 rtc::dchecked_cast<int>(restrictions_.max_pixels_per_frame().value_or(
163 std::numeric_limits<int>::max()));
164 wants.target_pixel_count =
165 restrictions_.target_pixels_per_frame().has_value()
166 ? absl::optional<int>(rtc::dchecked_cast<int>(
167 restrictions_.target_pixels_per_frame().value()))
168 : absl::nullopt;
169 wants.max_framerate_fps =
170 restrictions_.max_frame_rate().has_value()
171 ? static_cast<int>(restrictions_.max_frame_rate().value())
172 : std::numeric_limits<int>::max();
173 wants.resolution_alignment = resolution_alignment_;
174 wants.max_pixel_count =
175 std::min(wants.max_pixel_count,
176 rtc::dchecked_cast<int>(pixels_per_frame_upper_limit_.value_or(
177 std::numeric_limits<int>::max())));
178 wants.max_framerate_fps =
179 std::min(wants.max_framerate_fps,
180 frame_rate_upper_limit_.has_value()
181 ? static_cast<int>(frame_rate_upper_limit_.value())
182 : std::numeric_limits<int>::max());
183 wants.resolutions = resolutions_;
184 return wants;
185}
